@startuml ThesisManagementAPI-ActivityDiagram

title Thesis Management API - Student Finds a Tutor and Starts a Thesis

|Student|
start
:Login to the system;
:Search for subject areas by name (e.g., "Design");
:Receives a list of subject areas;
:Selects a subject areas;
:Searches for tutors covering the selected subject areas;
:Receives a list of tutors;
:Selects a tutor and views their profile;
:Contacts tutor and agrees on a thesis;
:Submits a new thesis proposal via API;

|System|
:Creates a new thesis with status "IN_DISCUSSION";
:Notifies the assigned tutor;

|Tutor|
:Receives notification;
:Reviews the thesis proposal;
:Updates the thesis status to "REGISTERED";

|Student|
:Receives notification of registration;
:Works on the thesis;
:Submits the final document;

|System|
:Updates thesis status to "SUBMITTED";
:Notifies the tutor;

|Tutor|
:Reviews and grades the thesis;
:Updates thesis status to "DEFENDED";

stop

@enduml
